khandvi is a gujarati recipe prepared with minimum oil and taste pleasing if served in breakfast.

00:00:17.208 --> 00:00:22.700
let's see what all ingredients are required for making khandvi.

00:00:23.618 --> 00:00:25.492
gram flour - 1 cup

00:00:25.908 --> 00:00:29.243
curd - 1 cup(whisked)

00:00:29.615 --> 00:00:33.242
salt - as per taste (3/4 tsp)

00:00:33.734 --> 00:00:36.543
turmeric powder- 1/4 tsp

00:00:37.340 --> 00:00:39.451
these to be used for making mixture.

00:00:39.780 --> 00:00:42.264
red mustard seeds - 1/2 tsp

00:00:42.744 --> 00:00:45.434
green chilly - 2-3 (finely chopped)

00:00:45.794 --> 00:00:50.571
coconut - 2 tbsp (grated)

00:00:51.219 --> 00:00:54.893
green coriander- 1 tbsp (chopped)

00:00:55.169 --> 00:00:57.391
oil - to make tadka

00:00:57.648 --> 00:01:01.243
these are to be used for tadka for khandvi.

00:01:01.740 --> 00:01:05.898
formaking khandvi make batter of gram flour.

00:01:06.363 --> 00:01:24.845
take gram flour,whisked curd,turmeric powder and salt in a bowl

00:01:27.087 --> 00:01:32.365
stir until all lumps get dissolved.

00:01:40.593 --> 00:01:43.847
now add 2 cups of water in this batter.

00:02:06.006 --> 00:02:16.371
stir again until batter gets smooth.

00:02:27.219 --> 00:02:30.235
we have added ginger paste along with curd.

00:02:34.386 --> 00:02:40.839
batter is ready,now we will make khandvi from it.

00:02:49.203 --> 00:03:03.673
add this batter in a utensil and cook for 9-10 minutes or until batter seperates from the utensil.

00:03:05.108 --> 00:03:09.013
cook the batter by stirring constantly.

00:03:16.895 --> 00:03:23.530
it take 9-10 minutes for cooking this much quantity of batter.

00:03:26.342 --> 00:03:35.283
batter is cooked now turn off the gas and set the batter.

00:03:39.339 --> 00:03:43.671
you can set the cooked batter of khandvi on any plain surface.

00:03:44.152 --> 00:03:51.076
like you can set it on this side or back side of a plate.

00:03:51.377 --> 00:03:57.370
you can also use melamine or steel tray or setting the batter.

00:03:57.813 --> 00:04:02.966
plain marbel surface can also be used for setting the batter.

